{"session_id": "20260315_121829_eb1f1679", "turn_index": 1, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T12:20:39.097142+00:00", "player_text": "你好", "npc_id": "npc_001", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max", "output": {"narration": "晨光村的草垛旁，阳光洒在你身上。村长艾琳娜拄着木杖，站在许愿井边，神情既关切又忧虑。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_001", "text": "啊，你终于醒了，孩子。我是村长艾琳娜。恶龙‘烬喉’已经烧毁了邻村……我们急需一位真正的勇者。你愿意承担这份使命吗？"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": "loc_001", "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [], "inventory_delta": {}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "玩家首次与村长艾琳娜对话，她介绍了当前危机并暗示屠龙使命。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_121829_eb1f1679:world_bible:-:-:-:-:4478a7d0", "20260315_121829_eb1f1679:location:-:loc_001:-:-:2b69ecf6", "20260315_121829_eb1f1679:npc_profile:npc_001:-:-:-:377defa9"], "retrieved_ids": [], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstore/20260315_121829_eb1f1679", "filters": [{"session_id": "20260315_121829_eb1f1679", "npc_id": "npc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_121829_eb1f1679", "location_id": "loc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {"session_id": "20260315_121829_eb1f1679", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}], "counts": {"always_include": 3, "retrieved": 0, "store_total": 19}}}
{"session_id": "20260315_121829_eb1f1679", "turn_index": 2, "timestamp": "2026-03-15T12:21:04.590872+00:00", "player_text": "我愿意", "npc_id": "npc_001", "location_id": "loc_001", "model_used": "qwen3-max", "output": {"narration": "艾琳娜眼中闪过一丝欣慰，但随即又恢复了谨慎的神情。她轻抚许愿井边的石沿，低声说道。", "npc_dialogue": [{"npc_id": "npc_001", "text": "你的心志让我看到了希望，孩子。但烬喉不是寻常野兽，贸然前往只会白白送命。我建议你先去迷雾森林寻找精灵向导瑟兰迪尔——他掌握着第一件圣物的线索。"}], "world_updates": {"player_location": null, "npc_moves": [], "flags_delta": {}, "quest_updates": {}, "quest_progress_updates": [{"quest_id": "quest_main_001", "title": null, "category": null, "status": null, "objective": null, "guidance": "前往迷雾森林（loc_002）寻找精灵向导瑟兰迪尔，获取森林圣徽的线索。", "giver_npc_id": null, "reward_hint": null, "required_items": {}, "reward_items": {}, "collected_items_delta": {}}, {"quest_id": "quest_side_001", "title": null, "category": null, "status": "active", "objective": null, "guidance": "在迷雾森林收集银叶草 x2、夜露蘑菇 x3 和古树树脂 x1，交给瑟兰迪尔。", "giver_npc_id": null, "reward_hint": null, "required_items": {}, "reward_items": {}, "collected_items_delta": {}}], "inventory_delta": {}, "npc_personality_updates": []}, "memory_summary": "玩家接受了屠龙使命，艾琳娜指引其前往迷雾森林寻找精灵向导瑟兰迪尔，并激活了相关任务指引。", "safety": {"refuse": false, "reason": null}}, "move_rejections": [], "move_refusals": [], "move_applied_count": 0, "move_rejected_count": 0, "move_refused_count": 0, "guard_warnings": [], "rag": {"enabled": true, "always_include_ids": ["20260315_121829_eb1f1679:world_bible:-:-:-:-:4478a7d0", "20260315_121829_eb1f1679:location:-:loc_001:-:-:2b69ecf6", "20260315_121829_eb1f1679:npc_profile:npc_001:-:-:-:377defa9", "20260315_121829_eb1f1679:memory:npc_001:loc_001:1:-:2168d808", "20260315_121829_eb1f1679:summary:-:-:1:-:60ff0ad3"], "retrieved_ids": [], "retrieval_backend": "persistent_hybrid", "embedding_backend": "hashing", "vectorstore_path": "data/vectorstore/20260315_121829_eb1f1679", "filters": [{"session_id": "20260315_121829_eb1f1679", "npc_id": "npc_001", "doc_type": ["memory", "summary", "lore"]}, {